# NOTE: CLAUDE.md and ANTIGRAVITY.md are intentionally TRACKED so AI-assistant
# context travels with the repo (maintainer request 2026-05-02). They contain
# absolute Windows paths under C:\Users\danjo\... — clones on other machines
# will need to adapt those paths. If you fork this repo, consider rewriting
# the path-bearing sections to your own layout.

# Steam SDK artifact
upload/steam_appid.txt
.temp/

# REVIEW (2026-05-01):
# - bundleV2/ is INTENTIONALLY tracked (so other devs / git bisect can see the built bundle
#   that was deployed at each commit). Confirm with maintainer; if accidentally tracked, add
#   `**/bundleV2/` here.
# - .vmbrc is tracked at repo root and contains absolute path to vmb tools — fine for solo
#   dev but if this repo is ever shared, would need a per-user override pattern.
# - bundleHistory.dat is tracked at repo root (binary, mtime old). Confirm intentional.
# - The 16-hex glob pattern correctly catches loose extensionless bundle artifacts but ALSO
#   catches any file with a 16-hex name in any directory (including bundleV2/ — but since
#   actual bundle files in bundleV2 have .mod_bundle extension, this is harmless).
# - dumps/ is tracked. Confirm intentional — these are large reference files generated from
#   in-game commands. Maybe `dumps/*.txt` should be ignored except a curated set?
# - launcher_screenshot.png (1MB) at repo root is tracked. Should it be moved to a docs/
#   subfolder?
# Sensitive paths check: no .env or credentials.json patterns ignored, but none exist in repo
# either. ugc_tool authenticates via Steam session, no token files written here.
